biography.text: Wildstylez has been at the pinnacle of the hardstyle scene for over a decade. He is a creative mastermind, a technical genius, a founding member of Project One - his timeless and eternal collaboration with Headhunterz - and he is already regarded as one of the all-time-greats of the genre. Through the years he has innovated, revolutionized and set countless benchmarks, all to delight his adoring fanbase. With countless gigs in his schedule and copious amounts of new music still to come, Wildstylez is set to remain at the very peak of the hardstyle mountain.
